# 🚀 Automation Playwright Java 2026

## 📌 Overview
This repository contains an end-to-end **Test Automation Framework** built with **Playwright + Java**, designed for scalable, maintainable, and high-performance UI testing.

The framework follows modern automation best practices such as **Page Object Model (POM)**, **parallel execution**, and **CI/CD integration**, helping QA engineers build reliable and fast test suites.

---

## 🧰 Tech Stack
- **Language:** Java  
- **Automation Tool:** Playwright  
- **Build Tool:** Maven  
- **Test Framework:** TestNG / JUnit *(update if needed)*  
- **Reporting:** Allure / Extent Reports *(update if you use)*  
- **CI/CD:** GitHub Actions  

---

## ✨ Features
- ✅ Cross-browser testing (Chromium, Firefox, WebKit)  
- ✅ Page Object Model (POM) structure  
- ✅ Parallel test execution  
- ✅ Screenshot & video recording on failure  
- ✅ Auto-wait mechanism (no hard waits)  
- ✅ Config-driven environment setup  
- ✅ CI/CD integration ready  

---

## 📁 Project Structure
```bash
Automation-Playwright-Java-2026/
│── src/
│   ├── main/java/
│   │   ├── pages/          # Page Objects
│   │   ├── utils/          # Utilities & helpers
│   │   └── config/         # Configuration
│   │
│   ├── test/java/
│   │   ├── tests/          # Test cases
│   │   └── base/           # Base test setup
│
│── .github/workflows/      # CI/CD pipeline
│── pom.xml                 # Dependencies
│── README.md
